0831/41/ |website=OOC |accessdate=October 18, 2018 |date=August 31, 2018}}\n*{{cite web |title=Filter: Scottish Singles Sales Chart Top 100 |url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/scottish-singles-chart/ |website=OOC |accessdate=March 1, 2020 |date=February 28, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"2\"| KOR\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"|[[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br /><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.officialcharts.com/artist/48781/bts/ |title=BTS {{!}} Full Official Chart History |publisher=[[Official Charts Company]] |accessdate=January 15, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"|[[Billboard Hot 100|US]]<br><ref name=\"hot100\">{{cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/music/BTS/chart-history/HSI |title=BTS Chart History: Billboard Hot 100 |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |accessdate=March 3, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:3.5em;font-size:90%;\"|[[Billboard charts|US World]]<br /><ref>For peak positions on the US World Digital Songs Chart:\n*{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/world-digital-song-sales/2016-10-29|title=Lie (World Digital Songs)|website=Billboard}}\n*{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/world-digital-song-sales/2017-10-07|title=Serendipity (World Digital Songs)|website=Billboard}}\n*{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/world-digital-song-sales/2020-03-07|title=Filter (World Digital Songs)|website=Billboard}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3.5em;font-size:90%;\"|[[Gaon Digital Chart|Gaon]]<br><ref>For peak positions on the South Korean Gaon Digital Chart:\n*{{Cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=42&hitYear=2016&termGbn=week|title=Lie|website=gaonchart.co.kr}}\n*{{Cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=38&hitYear=2017&termGbn=week|title=Intro : Serendipity|websit