5 graduation by Jimin & V of BTS |url=https://soundcloud.com/bangtan/95-graduation-by-jimin-v-of |website=[[Soundcloud]] |accessdate=October 19, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"Christmas Day\" by Jimin & [[Jungkook]]\n| Korean cover of [[Mistletoe (Justin Bieber song)|\"Mistletoe\" by Justin Bieber]]\n| <ref name = \"Christmas Day\">{{cite web |title=Christmas Day by Jimin, Jungkook of BTS |url=https://soundcloud.com/bangtan/christmas-day-by-jimin-jungkook-of-bts |website=Soundcloud |accessdate=October 23, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|2017\n|\"We Don't Talk Anymore Pt.2\" by Jimin & [[Jungkook]]\n|Cover of \"[[We Don't Talk Anymore (Charlie Puth song)|We Don't Talk Anymore]]\" by [[Charlie Puth]] and [[Selena Gomez]] \n|<ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n|2018\n|\"Promise\" {{small|(\uc57d\uc18d; ''Yaksok'')}}\n|{{n/a}}\n|<ref name=\"promise\">{{cite web|url=https://soundcloud.com/bangtan/firstjiminpresent|title=\uc57d\uc18d By JIMIN Of BTS|website=[[Soundcloud]]|date=December 31, 2018|accessdate=December 31, 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== Writing credits ===\nAll song credits are adapted from the [[Korea Music Copyright Association]]'s database, unless otherwise noted.<ref name=\"KMCA\">{{cite web|title=Songs Registered Under Jimin (10005241)|url=http://www.komca.or.kr/foreign2/eng/S01.jsp|website=komca.or.kr|accessdate=January 19, 2018}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:10em;\"|Year\n! style=\"width:10em;\"|Artist\n! style=\"width:19em;\"|Album\n! style=\"width:20em;\"|Song\n|-\n| 2013\n| rowspan=1| [[BTS]]\n| ''[[2 Cool 4 Skool]]''\n| \"Outro: Circle Room Cypher\"\n|- \n| 2014\n| Jimin & [[Jungkook]]\n| {{n/a|Non-album release}}\n| \"Christmas Day\"<ref name = \"Christmas Day\"/>\n|-\n| 2015\n| rowspan=2| BTS\n| ''[[The Most Beautiful Moment in Life, Part 1]]''\t\t\n| \"Boyz with Fun\"\t\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Wings (BTS album)|Wings]]''\n| \"Lie\"\n|-\n| 2018\n| Jimin\n| {{n/a|Non-album release}}\n| \"Promise\"<ref name=\"promise\" />\n|-\n| 2020\n| BTS\n| ''[[Map of